cu.explanation_en: Setting the integrity algorithm to the unknown enum 'nia4' will cause negotiation failure during the security negotiation phase and NAS registration rejection.

du.explanation_en: Setting the physical cell ID to an out-of-range value of 1008 will cause cell identification conflicts and prevent proper cell setup.
du.explanation_zh: 將物理細胞 ID 設定為超出範圍的值 1008，會導致細胞識別衝突，並阻止正確的細胞設置。
